<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>How should a society allocate and distribute its resources? Which needs should have the highest priority? Economists study how people use limited resources to satisfy their unlimited wants. They create scientific models to explain why people behave the way they do and use these models along with observations to analyze and explain why things happen the way they do. Based on this knowledge, they can propose solutions to problems.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
